OL,3,CVeteran thrown out of Navy for being
OL,4,Cgay 'elated' as compensation announced
OL,6,FMr Hammond told ITV News West Country
OL,7,Fhe is "chuffed" by the announcement.
OL,9,F"It's about time," he said. "I'm quite
OL,10,Felated about it."
OL,12,FVeterans who were dismissed or
OL,13,Fdischarged because of their sexual
OL,14,Forientation or gender identity are to
OL,15,Freceive #50,000.
OL,17,FPersonnel who were "negatively
OL,18,Faffected" by the ban during their time
OL,19,Fin the service between 1967 and 2000
OL,20,Fwill be given up to another #20,000,
OL,21,Fthe ministry said.
