OL,3,CVeteran thrown out of Navy for being
OL,4,Cgay 'elated' as compensation announced
OL,6,FLast year, a review found that
OL,7,Ftreatment of LGBT personnel and
OL,8,Fveterans in the Armed Forces was
OL,9,F'completely unacceptable' and 'highly
OL,10,Fregrettable'.
OL,12,F"We've lost quite a lot not just in
OL,13,Fwages but in dignity and liberty and
OL,14,Fso forth," Mr Hammond said.
OL,16,FHe said a huge amount of stress and
OL,17,Fshame was put on people, adding: "I
OL,18,Fdon't think you can ever really
OL,19,Fcompensate for that feeling of shame
OL,20,Fthat was put on you."
