OL,3,CVeteran thrown out of Navy for being
OL,4,Cgay 'elated' as compensation announced
OL,6,FMr Hammond joined the Royal Navy in
OL,7,F1981 at the age of 17, when being gay
OL,8,Fin the armed forces was forbidden.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV News previously at his
OL,11,Fhome in Plymouth, Mr Hammond said: "I
OL,12,Fwas good at my job. Very good at my
OL,13,Fjob. I had an exemplary record.
OL,15,F"I kept my private life very private,
OL,16,FI didn't involve it in my work at all.
OL,17,FBut the military police came to arrest
OL,18,Fme.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
