OL,3,CVeteran thrown out of Navy for being
OL,4,Cgay 'elated' as compensation announced
OL,6,F"They did the Mr Nice and Mr Nasty
OL,7,Froutine on me - you've got one person
OL,8,Fsaying 'If you co-operate...' and
OL,9,Fanother being quite direct. In the end
OL,10,FI did cave and say, 'Yeah, I am gay.'"
OL,12,FMartyn says he was arrested, court-
OL,13,Fmartialled and held in detention
OL,14,Fquarters at the Portsmouth Naval
OL,15,FBarracks, then sent to a corrective
OL,16,Ftraining camp for 40 days.
OL,18,FHe was dismissed from the Navy and
OL,19,Fsuffered a mental breakdown. "It's the
OL,20,Fworst feeling in the world," he said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
