OL,3,CVeteran thrown out of Navy for being
OL,4,Cgay 'elated' as compensation announced
OL,6,FHe described the compensation being
OL,7,Foffered as a "really good figure" but
OL,8,Fsaid questions remain about whether
OL,9,Fpeople will have the pensions they
OL,10,Fmissed out on reinstated.
OL,12,F"If I got my pension reinstated, I
OL,13,Fknow that I can retire with piece of
OL,14,Fmind," Mr Hammond told ITV News.
OL,15,F"Obviously I got my state pension and
OL,16,Fa tiny bit of my private pension but
OL,17,Fby getting some of my military
OL,18,Fpension, I can retire knowing I'll be
OL,19,Fokay."
