OL,3,CVeteran thrown out of Navy for being
OL,4,Cgay 'elated' as compensation announced
OL,6,FDefence Secretary John Healey said:
OL,7,F"The historic treatment of LGBT
OL,8,Fveterans was a moral stain on our
OL,9,Fnation. Our Government is determined
OL,10,Fto right the wrongs of the past and
OL,11,Frecognise the hurt that too many
OL,12,Fendured.
OL,14,F"We have listened to veterans and will
OL,15,Fcontinue to deliver against the
OL,16,Frecommendations set out in the
OL,17,FEtherton review. We will continue to
OL,18,Fsupport our veterans as we work to
OL,19,Frenew the nation's contract with those
OL,20,Fwho serve, and have served.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
